{
  "stem": "11844.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My life in the Werkdorp Nieuwesluis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have chosen to become a night watchman there, and my duties were to go around to be sure there were no fire-- no fires.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there were many little wooden barracks, where the young boys and young girls slept, and there was a big house where general things took place.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to be sure that the fires in the-- the-- the stoves in the barracks were out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was a night watchman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Studying, learning, playing chess, listen to good music, and studying, studying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at 5:00 in the morning, I had to wake up the boys and the girls who had service milking the cows.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a terrible thing to go in those barracks where there were seven or eight girls sleeping, and wake two or three of them-- wake up two or three of them who had early kitchen service or-- or milking service.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I met many guys there who were a little but older than I am, who had partially college education.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would say, I have always referred to-- and I have said it many times in Holland after the war-- that Werkdorp Nieuwesluis for me was a mini university, a mini college.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That is where I did 80% to 90% of my self-educating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I fell in love with a wonderful Austrian girl by the name of Sonja Reich.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was born 1919, so she was three years younger, so I was-- no, six years younger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was 22 and she was about 16.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was 23, and she was 17.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she fell very much in love with her-- with me, I mean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I fell very much in love with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
